.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
City: miami, edinburgh, london, marseilles, colone
Transport: taxi, bus, subway, train, skateboard
Birthday: february, november, june, july, december
Game: backgammon, whist, monopoly, go, scrabble

1. City:miami == Color:red
2. City:edinburgh == Game:backgammon
3. Birthday:february == Color:green
4. City:london == Birthday:november
5. Color:green is to the right of Color:ivory
6. Transport:taxi == Game:scrabble
7. Transport:bus == Color:yellow
8. Birthday:june is in the middle
9. City:marseilles is on the far left
10. Transport:subway is on the left or right of Game:whist
11. Transport:bus is to the left or right of Game:go
12. Transport:train == Birthday:july
13. City:colone == Transport:skateboard
14. City:marseilles is to the left or right of Color:blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| City	|   marseilles	|    london	|     miami	|    edinburgh	|    colone	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Birthday	|     december	|      november	|      june	| july	|     february	|
| Transport		|     bus	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| train	|   parliament	|
| Game		|     whist	|     go	|     scrabble	|     backgammon	|     monopoly	|
